      },
      {
        "category": "summary",
        "text": "Successful exploitation of these vulnerabilities could lead to a server crashing, a denial-of-service condition, data leakage, or remote code execution.\u00a0",
        "title": "Risk evaluation"
      },
      {
        "category": "other",
        "text": "CRITICAL INFRASTRUCTURE SECTORS: Critical Manufacturing\u00a0",
        "title": "Critical infrastructure sectors"
      },
      {
